                <p dir="ltr">Season 2 is now live in <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/games/marvel-rivals/" data-ref-id="5000-624043">Marvel Rivals</a>. Emma Frost makes her debut in the game with a season themed around her Hellfire Gala on the mutant island known as Krakoa. In addition to new seasonal content, the patch notes address several map and hero-related bugs. The update also adds a gifting feature for cosmetics.</p><p dir="ltr">Content wise, Marvel Rivals update version 20250411 adds Hellfire Gala: Krakoa as the new Domination map and Emma Frost as a new playable hero. In addition to her standard white outfit, Emma comes with two additional costume choices: X-Revolution and Blue Sapphire.</p><div tabindex="0" data-id="562923" data-promo-id="0" data-user-has-ads="1" data-video="{&quot;id&quot;:6465875,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Marvel%20Rivals%20-%20Season%202%20Battle%20Pass%3A%20Flower%20of%20Krakoa%20Official%20Trailer&quot;,&quot;lengthSeconds&quot;:69,&quot;startTime&quot;:0,&quot;autoplay&quot;:false,&quot;share&quot;:{&quot;linkUrl&quot;:&quot;https://www.gamespot.com/videos/marvel-rivals-season-2-battle-pass-flower-of-krakoa-official-trailer/2300-6465875/&quot;,&quot;embedUrl&quot;:&quot;https://www.gamespot.com/videos/embed/6465875/&quot;,&quot;embedHtml&quot;:{&quot;640&quot;:&quot;









